  EffectDiscription_ENG: "When you would play this card from your hand, reduce the
    play cost by 4 for every 10 cards in your trash.[All Turns][Once Per Turn] When
    a card is trashed from your deck, you may play 1 [Impmon] from your trash without
    paying the cost. The Digimon played by this effect gains \uFF1CRush\uFF1E for
    the turn.[Opponent's Turn] When an opponent's Digimon attacks, trash the top
    card of your deck."
